   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-d" mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>(马尔肯兴奋地说)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$王城近卫兵马尔肯$<BR>我心中的光和太阳！我日夜思念的<FONT color=#a82424>贵族</FONT>小姐！<BR>我鼓起勇气向她表白，还送给了她昂贵的<FONT color=#a82424>宝石项链</FONT>。你不知道我有多紧张。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-e" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>再不回去的话，就要被当成逃兵了。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$王城近卫兵马尔肯$<BR>我说如果可以接受我的心意，就带着<FONT color=#a82424>项链</FONT>，到这里来和我见面。<BR>
即使不答应……希望也能到这里来当面拒绝我。所以我要一直等下去！</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-f" mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>(马尔肯陷入了苦恼)</html>]]></talk_answer>
